---

## 🔬 Bioinformatics Relevance

Variant annotation is an important step in **NGS (Next Generation Sequencing) pipelines**.
Tools like **ClinVar, ANNOVAR, and VEP** are commonly used to determine the **clinical significance of genetic mutations**.

This project demonstrates the **basic concept behind such tools**.

---

